name: uTrade
description: uTrade is a financial trading platform designed to improve access to digital asset markets through artificial intelligence and blockchain technology. It provides AI-driven trading bots, copy trading, futures grid strategies, and market signal groups. The native token, UTT, has a total supply of 50 million and functions as a utility token for platform features, governance, and rewards. The ecosystem also includes profit-sharing NFTs and a buyback-and-burn mechanism to support long-term value.
